## Naming conventions

| Artifact | Convention | Example |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| DB key constant | `<Entity>_DbKey` | `Organization_DbKey` |
| DB type | `DB_<Entity>` | `DB_Organization` |
| Prototype type | `DatabaseDef_<Entity>` | `DatabaseDef_Organization` |
| UI type | `UI_<Entity>` | `UI_Organization` |
| Database constant | `DBDef_<Entity>` | `DBDef_Organization` |
| Modifiable validator | `<Entity>_modifiablePropsValidator` | `Organization_modifiablePropsValidator` |
| Generated validator | `<Entity>_generatedPropsValidator` | `Organization_generatedPropsValidator` |
| BE module class | `ModuleBE_<Entity>DB_Class` | `ModuleBE_OrganizationDB_Class` |
| BE module singleton | `ModuleBE_<Entity>DB` | `ModuleBE_OrganizationDB` |
| BE module pack | `ModulePackBE_<Entity>` | `ModulePackBE_Tag` |
| FE module class | `ModuleFE_<Entity>_Class` | `ModuleFE_Tag_Class` |
| FE module singleton | `ModuleFE_<Entity>` | `ModuleFE_Tag` |
| FE module pack | `ModulePackFE_<LibName>` | `ModulePackFE_PromptTagging` |
